atmbranchfinderspring.resourceserver.validation.accesstokens

Interface TokenValidator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccountRequestAuthorizationValidator, GrantValidator, PermissionValidator, TokenIsNotExpired, TokenTypeValidator

    public interface TokenValidator
    TokenValidator interface follows the Command Pattern. Whenever an access token is checked, a list of these validators is created to check if every requirement is fulfilled.
